{"tid":54012,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"同女朋友嘈交 覺得希望近了","createTime":"2016-12-25T07:53:24.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-25T10:29:17.000Z","uid":5190,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4ed181327c8b5ba881a735d212fc94e674d084c3","tid":54012,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T07:53:24.000Z","msg":"我平安夜已經陪左佢成晚 我想聖誕節同班兄弟出去玩下姐 佢咁都唔比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 驚死我同啲朋友互屌咁 大佬 全男班你驚乜撚呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n講到依個地步我都無晒計 原來佢咁撚專制 比一日我都唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n平時你要食咩 去邊 邊日要陪你我都就晒你 我啲fd話我係一等一好男人 連同佢地踢波嘅時間都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一齊左啱啱好一年 我都就左你一年 年尾你令到我地嘈交 我諗都完架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n各位 我又恢復自由啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83fa2df531a5b62f5e2a14588cdeed69eb7512de","tid":54012,"uid":384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T07:55:38.000Z","msg":"Same here<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 琴日散左仲心痛緊"},{"pid":"d71adc4265b1d466ba8c51a52064a22d6387d0a9","tid":54012,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T07:58:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Same here<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 琴日散左仲心痛緊</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n自由啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e2f2515b8758590b3a6123091604f1fba27f89d","tid":54012,"uid":24063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T07:59:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/25/155914_c69b8b38e44ba4466cbb1cd8129de96b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F25%2F155914_c69b8b38e44ba4466cbb1cd8129de96b.jpg&h=7023cf6b&s={SIZE}\